SIGNATURES Pursuant to the requirements of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934, the Registrant has duly caused this report to be signed on its behalf by the undersigned thereunto duly authorized. Date: October 5, 2005 ACUITY BRANDS, INC. By: /s/ Kenyon W. Murphy ----------------------------------------------- Kenyon W. Murphy Senior Vice President and General Counsel
