On December 1, 2008, Acuity Brands, Inc. issued a press release announcing that it has commenced a cash tender offer to purchase any and all of its outstanding 6% Notes due 2009 (the "Notes"). As of December 1, 2008, the aggregate principal amount of Notes outstanding was $160 million. A copy of the press release is attached hereto as Exhibit 99.1 and is incorporated herein by reference in its entirety.
 
 
 
