(c) The Parties expressly waive and forego any right to recover punitive, exemplary, lost profits, consequential, incidental, indirect, special or similar damages, or damages measured by a multiple, in any arbitration, lawsuit, litigation or proceeding arising out of or resulting from any controversy or claim arising out of or relating to this Agreement or the transactions contemplated hereby.
