Item 8.01. Other Events.
On January 22, 2010, Acuity Brands, Inc. issued a press release announcing its intention to redeem all of the remaining $24,255,000 in aggregate principal amount of its outstanding 8.375% Senior Notes due 2010 (CUSIP No. 00508YAB8) (the "Notes") on February 23, 2010. Following such redemption there will not be any Notes outstanding. A copy of the press release relating to the announcement is attached hereto as Exhibit 99.1 and is incorporated herein by reference.
Item 9.01. Financial Statements and Exhibits.
 
 
