Acuity Brands, Inc., is a North American market leader and one of the world's leading providers of luminaires, lighting control systems and related products and services with fiscal year 2010 net sales of over $1.6 billion. The Company's lighting and system control product lines include Lithonia Lighting, Holophane, Peerless, Mark Architectural Lighting, Hydrel, American
 
Electric Lighting , Gotham , Carandini , RELOC , MetalOptics , Antique Street Lamps, Tersen , Synergy Lighting Controls, Sensor Switch, Lighting Control & Design, and ROAM. Headquartered in Atlanta, Georgia, Acuity Brands employs approximately 6,000 associates and has operations throughout North America, Europe and Asia.
